{"tid":843367,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬納當拿勸美斯退出國家隊","createTime":"2018-10-01T05:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T06:58:27.000Z","uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7b261e592bd727cbc0985147b4c50487c82adeb8","tid":843367,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"艾馬利：藍斯續約與否都會出力比賽<br />\n阿根廷在世盃16強出局後，領隊森派奧利被炒，暫時由史卡朗尼當上暫代領隊，但美斯在最近兩次國家隊點兵均未有入選，他亦沒有就是否退役一事表態。<br />\n不過馬納當拿便認為美斯應該退出國家隊︰「我勸他退役不要回來，他一直成為責怪對象，便索性不要回來看看國家隊可變成怎樣。」<br />\n<br />\n「美斯是世界冠軍，不應該是責怪的目標，你可以對他寄予厚望，但國家隊沒有為他做任何事，沒有熱情。」<br />\n同時他更批評暫代領隊史卡朗尼︰「他是個蠢才，我離開時把10號球衣交予美斯，現在美斯沒有比賽亦應如此，把10號懸空十分荒謬。他說自己已準備好接掌國家隊，但他沒有為阿根廷射入過一球，我不支持他接替此職務。」"},{"pid":"bf5baa8dde76302a98402a73a7cb2e627da52091","tid":843367,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:03:05.000Z","msg":"Argentina without messi.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b9620628a29791bfbda248352bd4878bc4e95d","tid":843367,"uid":146435,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:18:02.000Z","msg":"美斯阻撚住美沙上位"},{"pid":"476ffb8a109c394c31ebeedb9fd023db492cd3d6","tid":843367,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:38:03.000Z","msg":"又啪左藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6baeafe6c4f216a2881b0c66fa5a55375588c04","tid":843367,"uid":66593,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:38:37.000Z","msg":"廢老阻撚住我地呢班阿甲仔上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf1829ccc675a509c1a526ff67ebbf82eccba1f","tid":843367,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T06:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15919e1b694dc9eb6a4cd65dc51c64283a4ad806","tid":843367,"uid":34293,"like":0,"disli